answerText: Williamsburg[10] Williamsburg is bounded to the south by this river. This river contains U Thant Island and is also spanned by the Williamsburg and Brooklyn Bridges.

question: Question:  [10] Name this neighborhood of Brooklyn which contains the abandoned Domino sugar refinery. It also has notable Puerto Rican and Italian enclaves, although it is being gentrified by young white people.
